===Pronunciation===
*[[w:IPA|IPA]]: /gʌŋ ˈhəʊ/
*[[w:SAMPA|SAMPA]]: /gVN 'h@U/
===Etymology===
World War II; [[Mandarin]] Chinese, ''gonghé'' ([[工]][[合]] ''gong'', work + ''hé'', together), an acroym for ''gōngyè hézuòshè'' ([[工業]][[合作社]], [[工业]][[合作社]] Chinese Industrial Cooperative Society).

===Adjective===
# very [[enthusiasm|enthusiastic]] or [[energy|energetic]]
#:''No matter how gung ho you are when you start, you will tire as you become mired in details.''

